  "text": "A number of systematic reviews on the use of TCZ in RA have recently been published, with many including meta-analyses of clinical trial data. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] These reviews have concentrated on outcomes including clinical efficacy (ACR20, ACR50, ACR70, and DAS28 remission), effect on radiographic progression, function, quality of life, and safety in over 2000 patients receiving TCZ at varying doses, in comparison to either placebo or an active comparator (often MTX). ",
